Description:
This is implementation of graph cut algorithm to seperate front and background of image. 
src/main.cpp where I am reading image and return output image
src/createMinCut.cpp where I have implemented graph cut algorithm.
GraphCutAlgorithm is done by calculating probability to differentiate between forward and background pixels and then make a cut
on it.

For Full reference Read P1.pdf


How to Run the Code
Prerequisites:

cmake, opencv


To compile in the lab
——————————

run ./lab_config.sh
cd build
make

To compile on your own machine
———

cd build/
cmake ../
make


To run
——

In the build folder:
./sc image1 new_width new_height image2

 
